**/Input Data/*.dta

# Exclude all country-specific files (we only need MEX)
**/fertility_*.csv
**/mortality_*.csv
**/net_migration_*.csv
**/netmigration_*.csv
**/population_*.csv
**/population_historical_*.dta
**/wage_*.csv
