**/affiliation_*.csv
**/disability_rates_*.csv
**/retirement_rates_*.csv
**/survivor_rates_*.csv
**/transitions_*.dta
**/job_entry_model_*.ster
**/job_exit_model_*.ster
**/lifecycle_*.ster

# But KEEP all MEX files (the exception)
!**/*MEX*

